Finance minister Enoch Godongwana tabled his 2022/23 budget on Wednesday afternoon. Senior economist at FNB, Siphamandla Mkhwanazi, says it  was a positive budget for the consumer. Listen: Mkhwanazi said this is critical for supporting the fragile economic recovery. EFF members handed a memorandum of demands to minister Godongwana after the speech. TimesLIVE